Evocation
Level: Ranger 3
Components: V, M
Casting Time: 1 Round
Range: Touch
Target: 1 Arrow or Bolt
Duration: 1 round per level
Save: None
Spell Resistance: Yes

This spell is cast upon a arrow or bolt, engulfing its head in blackfire. In addition to taking normal damage from the missile, the target takes 2d6 fire damage as well and continues to burn for two more rounds from the flames.

